    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
      href="usb-printer-kernel.xml"/>

    <para>
      If you have a parallel printer, enable the following options in your
      kernel configuration and recompile the kernel:
    </para>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
